      "content": "Hey, I'm a trainer and I'm starting to work with some new clients from various ethnic backgrounds. I want to make sure my programming is as efficient as possible. Are there any actual biological differences in things like muscle fiber composition or natural athletic potential between different racial groups that I should keep in mind when tailoring their workouts?",
